1
00:00:45,250 --> 00:00:48,448
Come, sorrow.We welcome thee.
来吧，悲伤，我们欢迎你

2
00:00:48,515 --> 00:00:50,459
Let us join in grief,
让我们一起感受不幸

3
00:00:50,533 --> 00:00:52,639
rejoice in despair,
绝望让我们欣喜

4
00:00:52,710 --> 00:00:55,264
and honor the fortunate dead.
为侥幸的死亡而荣耀

5
00:00:55,335 --> 00:00:58,184
Dearly beloved...
亲爱的

6
00:01:40,514 --> 00:01:43,582
Good show, old man.
表现的不错，老家伙

7
00:01:43,652 --> 00:01:44,580
Gomez.

8
00:01:44,644 --> 00:01:46,172
Cara mia?

9
00:01:46,244 --> 00:01:47,391
Marvelous news.
美妙的惊喜

10
00:01:47,461 --> 00:01:49,851
I'm going to have a baby...
我要生孩子了

11
00:01:49,928 --> 00:01:51,138
right now.
就现在

12
00:01:57,036 --> 00:01:59,371
Nurse, how close are the contractions?
护士，宫缩频率是多少？

13
00:01:59,436 --> 00:02:01,030
Every 15 seconds, Doctor.
每15秒，医生

14
00:02:01,101 --> 00:02:02,858
Are you in unbearable pain?
你现在是否处于无法忍受的痛苦？

15
00:02:02,926 --> 00:02:05,797
Is it inhuman? My darling, is it torture?
残酷吗？亲爱的，是否备受折磨？

16
00:02:05,872 --> 00:02:07,247
Oui.

17
00:02:09,458 --> 00:02:11,664
And then mommy kissed daddy,
然后妈咪亲吻爸爸

18
00:02:11,732 --> 00:02:13,675
and the angel told the stork.
然后天使告诉鹳鸟

19
00:02:13,749 --> 00:02:15,692
The stork flew down from heaven
鹳鸟从天堂降临

20
00:02:15,766 --> 00:02:20,024
and left a diamond under a leaf in the cabbage patch,
留下一颗钻石在布袋里的叶子下面

21
00:02:20,089 --> 00:02:23,669
and the diamond turned into a baby.
然后钻石变成了一个宝宝

22
00:02:23,739 --> 00:02:26,556
Our parents are having a baby, too.
我们的父母也有宝宝了

23
00:02:26,621 --> 00:02:29,044
They had sex.
他们做爱了

24
00:02:29,117 --> 00:02:30,547
Push, Mrs. Addams.
用力，亚当斯夫人

25
00:02:32,607 --> 00:02:34,015
Forceps!
镊子！

26
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,063
Forceps.
镊子！

27
00:02:35,137 --> 00:02:37,026
Forceps!
镊子！

28
00:02:37,091 --> 00:02:38,040
Aah!

29
00:02:42,021 --> 00:02:44,193
Would you like anesthesia?
你需要麻醉嘛？

30
00:02:44,263 --> 00:02:46,817
No, thank you. But ask the children.
不，谢谢，不过你可以问问孩子

31
00:02:46,888 --> 00:02:48,264
Cara mia.

32
00:02:48,329 --> 00:02:50,599
Mon cher.

33
00:02:50,666 --> 00:02:52,041
Mrs. Addams, the baby?
亚当斯夫人，孩子？

34
00:02:52,107 --> 00:02:54,083
Pardon.
原谅我

35
00:02:54,156 --> 00:02:56,230
- It's a boy. - It's a girl.
-那是男孩 -那是女孩

36
00:02:57,262 --> 00:02:59,118
- Gomez! - What news?
怎么样了？

37
00:02:59,183 --> 00:03:00,264
Father, what is it?
爸爸，怎么样了？

38
00:03:00,336 --> 00:03:02,826
It's an Addams!
那是一个亚当斯！

39
00:03:45,162 --> 00:03:47,749
I've arranged a little surprise,my dearest.
我安排了一个小小的惊喜，我最亲爱的

40
00:03:47,820 --> 00:03:50,276
I hope you like it.
我希望你喜欢

41
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:13,268
Oh, Gomez, it's dark,it's depressing, it's desolate.
哦Gomez，它是多么黑暗，阴沉，凄凉

42
00:04:13,338 --> 00:04:14,997
It says, "toddler."
这是婴儿房

43
00:04:15,067 --> 00:04:16,345
It's a dream.
这是一个梦

44
00:04:16,412 --> 00:04:17,820
Come, cara mia.
来吧cara mia

45
00:04:19,677 --> 00:04:22,713
The Addams cradle.
这是小亚当斯的摇篮

46
00:04:36,487 --> 00:04:38,693
Welcome home, my son.
欢迎回家，我的儿子

47
00:04:40,299 --> 00:04:41,990
That's not true.
这不是真的

48
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:43,849
Everyone knows it is.
所有人都知道

49
00:04:43,916 --> 00:04:47,234
When you have a new baby,one of the other children has to die.
当你有了一个新的孩子，其余中的一个必须死

50
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:50,607
- Really?- It's a tradition. One of us has to go.
-真的？-这是传统，我们中的一个必须死

51
00:04:50,672 --> 00:04:53,576
Which one?
哪一个？

52
00:04:53,650 --> 00:04:55,593
Well, they only need one boy.
他们只需要一个男孩子

53
00:04:59,412 --> 00:05:01,236
He has my father's eyes.
他有我父亲的眼睛

54
00:05:01,302 --> 00:05:04,021
Gomez, take those out of his mouth.
Gomez,把那些东西从他嘴里拿走

55
00:05:04,088 --> 00:05:05,812
Coochie coochie coo.

56
00:05:05,881 --> 00:05:08,217
A baby in the house.
一个宝宝在这个房子里

57
00:05:08,283 --> 00:05:11,765
It's about time. Hey, kiddo.
这是 时间问题，嘿，老兄

58
00:05:12,893 --> 00:05:15,316
Did you see that?
你看到了嘛?

59
00:05:18,752 --> 00:05:22,071
He's a real devil.
他是真正的魔鬼

60
00:05:28,358 --> 00:05:30,726
Pugsley, the baby weighs 10 pounds.
Pugsley，孩子重10磅

61
00:05:30,791 --> 00:05:32,767
The cannonball weighs 20 pounds.
炮弹重20磅

62
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,231
Which will hit the stone walkway first?
哪个会先砸到石廊？

63
00:05:35,305 --> 00:05:36,965
I'm still on fractions.
不知道

64
00:05:37,035 --> 00:05:38,792
Which do you think?
你觉得是哪个?

65
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:40,170
The cannonball?
炮弹？

66
00:05:40,237 --> 00:05:43,752
Very good. But which one will bounce?
但是哪个会弹回来？

67
00:05:43,823 --> 00:05:45,678
The baby?
孩子？

68
00:05:45,744 --> 00:05:48,167
There's only one way to find out.
只有一个方法可以知道

69
00:05:48,242 --> 00:05:49,803
Ready?
准备？

70
00:05:51,316 --> 00:05:52,396
1...

71
00:05:52,467 --> 00:05:53,581
2...

72
00:05:53,653 --> 00:05:55,661
3.

73
00:05:55,733 --> 00:05:57,490
What a glorious evening.
多么美好的夜晚

74
00:05:57,558 --> 00:05:59,502
Rain.
下雨

75
00:06:06,172 --> 00:06:07,350
Cara mia.

76
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:08,369
Oh, dear.
哦，亲爱的

77
00:06:14,144 --> 00:06:17,080
Children,why do you hate the baby?
孩子们，你们为什么讨厌宝宝？

78
00:06:17,154 --> 00:06:20,025
We just want to play with him.
我们只想跟他玩

79
00:06:20,099 --> 00:06:21,988
Especially his head.
特别是他的头

80
00:06:22,053 --> 00:06:24,738
Do you think we love the baby more than you?
你们是不是认为我们爱宝宝多过爱你们？

81
00:06:24,806 --> 00:06:25,854
- Yes.- Yes.
是的

82
00:06:25,927 --> 00:06:28,317
Do you think when a new baby arrives,
你们是不是认为当一个新的宝宝来到这里

83
00:06:28,392 --> 00:06:29,920
another child has to die?
另一个就必须死？

84
00:06:29,994 --> 00:06:31,239
- Yes.- Yes.
是的

85
00:06:31,307 --> 00:06:33,380
Well,that's just not true.
好，那不是真的

86
00:06:34,957 --> 00:06:36,202
Not anymore.
不再是了

87
00:06:36,270 --> 00:06:38,989
It's just sibling rivalry.
这只是兄弟间的竞争

88
00:06:39,056 --> 00:06:43,335
Gomez, do you remember what we were like?
Gomez，你还记得我们是怎么样的吗？

89
00:06:43,409 --> 00:06:45,996
- I hated you!- I despised you.
-我讨厌你！-我鄙视你！

90
00:06:46,067 --> 00:06:49,331
I choked him till he lost consciousness
我把他掐昏

91
00:06:49,397 --> 00:06:51,602
and had to be put on a respirator.
必须急救为止

92
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:53,427
I tied him to a tree
我把他绑在树上

93
00:06:53,495 --> 00:06:55,918
and pulled out four of his permanent teeth.
拔了他四个牙

94
00:06:55,992 --> 00:06:57,782
When he was asleep,
当他睡觉的时候

95
00:06:57,850 --> 00:07:01,430
I opened his skull and removed his brains.
敲开他的头把他的脑子取出来

96
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:02,745
You did?
你做过？

97
00:07:05,822 --> 00:07:09,173
A brother!
兄弟！

98
00:07:09,248 --> 00:07:10,427
Brother!
兄弟！

99
00:07:20,423 --> 00:07:23,075
Children, you see?
孩子们，看到了嘛？

100
00:07:46,710 --> 00:07:48,882
"Death! Death to the enemies
把死亡带给敌人

101
00:07:48,951 --> 00:07:50,927
of the people of the republic."
为了人民 为了共和国

102
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,528
Hoorah!

103
00:07:52,602 --> 00:07:54,457
Justice is served.
正义得到了声张

104
00:07:54,523 --> 00:07:56,794
Bring forward the evil one.
把罪犯带上来

105
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:10,849
[La Marseillaise Plays]
马赛曲选段

106
00:08:17,447 --> 00:08:20,068
You have betrayed the people of France.
你背叛了法国人民

107
00:08:20,138 --> 00:08:21,829
You are evil incarnate.
你是罪恶的化身

108
00:08:21,898 --> 00:08:23,809
How do you plead?
你如何辩护

109
00:08:23,884 --> 00:08:25,707
[Pugsley] Guilty.
有罪

110
00:08:25,773 --> 00:08:28,044
Guilty by her own admission.
有罪，她自己承认了

111
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:29,604
The sentence is death.
判决处死

112
00:08:29,679 --> 00:08:33,030
Executioner,place her on the block.
侩子手，把他放到闸刀上

113
00:08:44,407 --> 00:08:46,131
1...

114
00:08:46,201 --> 00:08:47,926
2...

115
00:08:47,994 --> 00:08:50,416
Children,what are you doing?
孩子们，你们在干什么？

116
00:08:50,491 --> 00:08:51,605
- Playing!- Playing!
玩！

117
00:08:51,676 --> 00:08:52,603
3!

118
00:08:56,191 --> 00:08:58,842
Woe to the republic.
国家的不幸

119
00:09:00,001 --> 00:09:01,944
Look at you.
看看你

120
00:09:02,018 --> 00:09:05,053
Midnight, moonlight,
午夜，月光

121
00:09:05,123 --> 00:09:07,842
surrounded by death.
被死亡环绕

122
00:09:07,909 --> 00:09:09,666
It's been too long.
太久了

123
00:09:09,734 --> 00:09:12,256
Do it!
Hold him still!
动手！扶住他！

124
00:09:12,328 --> 00:09:13,506
[Gunshot,Glass Breaking]

125
00:09:13,576 --> 00:09:14,559
You missed.
你射偏了！

126
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:20,234
Here, catch!
这里，抓着！

127
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:22,406
I don't want him!
我不要他

128
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,419
One house,three children.
一座房子，三个孩子

129
00:09:25,487 --> 00:09:26,982
So many windows.
那么多窗子

130
00:09:27,056 --> 00:09:29,545
My darling, it's you I'm worried about,
我亲爱的，我很担心你

131
00:09:29,618 --> 00:09:31,179
the stress,all this squabbling.
压力和争吵

132
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:33,040
Oh, I'll be fine.
哦，我还好

133
00:09:33,108 --> 00:09:36,525
I'm just like any modern woman,trying to have it all--
我觉得现代点的女性应该可以解决

134
00:09:36,598 --> 00:09:38,192
loving husband, a family.
丈夫，家庭

135
00:09:38,263 --> 00:09:40,753
It's just I wish I had more time
我希望我有更多时间

136
00:09:40,824 --> 00:09:42,767
to seek out the dark forces
寻找出黑暗的力量

137
00:09:42,841 --> 00:09:46,618
and join their hellish crusade,that's all.
参加他们地狱一般的战争，就这样

138
00:09:46,683 --> 00:09:50,001
You can! You shall!So it must be!
你可以这么做！就应该这么做！

139
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:53,184
But how?
但是要如何？

140
00:09:53,311 --> 00:09:55,483
Children,as your new nanny,
孩子们，作为你们的新保姆

141
00:09:55,552 --> 00:09:58,140
I know that we're all concerned
我知道我们都关心

142
00:09:58,211 --> 00:09:59,641
about the environment,
环境

143
00:09:59,716 --> 00:10:03,514
so this morning, let's discuss
所以今天早晨，我们来谈谈

144
00:10:03,589 --> 00:10:05,598
how to prevent forest fires.
如何预防森林火灾

145
00:10:05,671 --> 00:10:07,330
Prevent them?
预防？

146
00:10:08,392 --> 00:10:09,735
All right, children,
好，孩子们

147
00:10:09,801 --> 00:10:11,777
I've had it up to here.
这样

148
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:15,431
Now you just answer one simple question.
现在，你们回到一个简单的问题

149
00:10:15,501 --> 00:10:17,869
Where is that baby?
孩子在哪里？

150
00:10:17,934 --> 00:10:19,178
Which part?
哪个部分？

151
00:10:19,246 --> 00:10:20,971
Hello, kiddies.
你们好，孩子们

152
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:22,764
I'm Polly the puppet.
我是木偶波利

153
00:10:22,832 --> 00:10:25,255
What shall we do today?
我们今天应该做什么呢？

154
00:10:25,331 --> 00:10:29,195
I know. Let's all clean our rooms.
我知道，让我们来打扫房间

155
00:10:29,268 --> 00:10:31,179
Hello, Polly.
你好，波利

156
00:10:31,254 --> 00:10:33,197
I'll clean my room
我已经打扫了我的房间

157
00:10:33,271 --> 00:10:36,142
in exchange for your immortal soul.
为了交换你不朽的灵魂

158
00:10:44,221 --> 00:10:45,815
Hi. Addams residence?
嗨，这里的亚当斯家嘛？

159
00:10:45,886 --> 00:10:48,308
Ooh, it's old.
哦，真古老

160
00:10:50,593 --> 00:10:52,732
And big.
也很大

161
00:10:52,802 --> 00:10:54,625
Lurch.
摇摇欲坠

162
00:10:55,972 --> 00:10:59,586
Hi! Hi. I'm Debbie Jellinsky from the agency.
嗨，我是Debbie Jellinsky 从代理商那里来

163
00:10:59,654 --> 00:11:00,800
The agency?
代理？

164
00:11:00,871 --> 00:11:03,328
But they claimed no one else was available.
但是他们说没人有空

165
00:11:03,401 --> 00:11:05,256
They suggested a Doberman.
他们建议雇佣一条猎狗

166
00:11:05,322 --> 00:11:07,624
Surprise!I've been out of town.
惊喜，我刚从镇上回来

167
00:11:07,690 --> 00:11:09,000
Are you the mom?
你是妈妈？

168
00:11:09,068 --> 00:11:10,530
I am Mrs. Addams.
我是亚当斯夫人

169
00:11:10,605 --> 00:11:14,251
I love your dress.It's so tight.
我喜欢你的裙子 很紧身

170
00:11:14,318 --> 00:11:15,432
Thank you.
谢谢

171
00:11:15,504 --> 00:11:17,960
Gomez.

172
00:11:18,033 --> 00:11:20,424
I believe we may have a new nanny...
我觉得我们有了一个新的保姆

173
00:11:20,498 --> 00:11:21,906
Miss Jellinsky.
Jellinsky小姐

174
00:11:21,972 --> 00:11:24,209
Deb.

175
00:11:24,276 --> 00:11:26,132
Isn't he a lady-killer?
他是位女性杀手嘛？

176
00:11:26,197 --> 00:11:28,435
Acquitted.
应该还不是

177
00:11:28,504 --> 00:11:30,447
I'll show you all my references
我会解释有关我的一切

178
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:32,245
so you'll know I'm not a homicidal maniac.
你会知道我不是杀人狂

179
00:11:32,313 --> 00:11:34,518
- Of course you're not.- You're too young.
当然你不是，你这么年轻

180
00:11:36,283 --> 00:11:37,877
Welcome to our home.
欢迎来我们家

181
00:11:37,948 --> 00:11:40,885
There's a belfry,a swamp,
一个钟楼，一片沼泽

182
00:11:40,958 --> 00:11:42,868
and a dungeon down below.
一条龙在下面

183
00:11:42,944 --> 00:11:45,727
- Cable?- Of course.
-锁起来了？-当然

184
00:11:45,793 --> 00:11:47,071
Debbie.

185
00:11:51,397 --> 00:11:53,918
Oh, is that the little critter?
哦，就是这个小畜牲？

186
00:11:53,989 --> 00:11:56,926
Oh, no. This is our baby.
哦，不，这个是我们的宝宝

187
00:11:56,999 --> 00:11:59,422
He's adorable. He's perfect. What's his name?
真可爱，他叫什么名字？

188
00:11:59,497 --> 00:12:00,926
It was agony.
非常苦恼

189
00:12:01,002 --> 00:12:03,338
We went through all the usual baby names...
我们试过了所有普通孩子的名字

190
00:12:03,403 --> 00:12:04,330
Lucifer...

191
00:12:04,396 --> 00:12:05,324
Benito...

192
00:12:05,388 --> 00:12:06,502
Mao.

193
00:12:06,573 --> 00:12:08,232
Then we came to our senses,
最后我们又来灵感

194
00:12:08,302 --> 00:12:09,994
something a child could live with...
一个适合孩子的

195
00:12:10,063 --> 00:12:11,111
Pubert.

196
00:12:11,184 --> 00:12:13,225
Pubert...

197
00:12:13,296 --> 00:12:14,672
I like it.
我喜欢他

198
00:12:14,738 --> 00:12:16,495
It's filthy.
真恶心

199
00:12:16,563 --> 00:12:17,644
May I?
可以吗？

200
00:12:17,716 --> 00:12:19,659
Your dress,is it flammable?
你的裙子易燃嘛？

201
00:12:19,733 --> 00:12:20,977
You've had your shots--
你注射疫苗了吗？

202
00:12:21,046 --> 00:12:23,534
measles, mumps, rabies?
麻疹，腮腺炎，狂犬病

203
00:12:29,690 --> 00:12:34,100
Oh, I just adore little babies.
哦，我喜欢这个小家伙

204
00:12:34,174 --> 00:12:37,853
I just want to squeeze them till there's not a breath left
我想捏的他喘不过气来

205
00:12:37,919 --> 00:12:39,708
in their tiny little bodies.
在他们的小身体上

